e)\n6. T-006: Router template (Deployment + Service)\n7. T-007: WM RBAC (SA + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding)\n8. T-008: Router RBAC (conditional SA + Role + RoleBinding)\n9. T-009: Volcano scheduler (conditional full set)\n10. T-010: Helper templates (_helpers.tpl)\n11. T-011: helm lint validation\n12. T-012: helm template rendering verification\n13. T-013: CRD verification\n14. T-014: kubectl dry-run validation\n15. T-015: Naming convention validation\n\n---\n\n### Summary of Key Absolute Paths\n\n| Category | Path |\n|----------|------|\n| Benchmark root | `/home/dsj/benchmark` |\n| Current workspace | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z` |\n| AR-030 change dir | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030` |\n| AR-030 design.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/design.md` |\n| AR-030 proposal.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/proposal.md` |\n| AR-030 tasks.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/tasks.md` |\n| AR-030 delta-spec.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md` |\n| AR-030 ST-3 log | `/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-030_ST-3.log` |\n| AR-030 ST-4 log | `/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-030_ST-4.log` |\n| Deployment spec | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/deployment/spec.md` |\n| Deployment design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/deployment/design.md` |\n| CI/CD spec | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/ci-cd/spec.md` |\n| CI/CD design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/ci-cd/design.md` |\n| Implementation plan | `/home/dsj/bench